ble","description":"John Wycliffe, English theologian and professor at the University of Oxford, completed a translation of the Bible from the Latin Vulgate into Middle English. This translation is known as Wycliffe's Bible and was completed around 1382.","url":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wycliffe%27s_Bible","urlTitle":"Wikipedia - Wycliffe's Bible","jurisdictionLevel":1}],"lifeSummary":"When William Stighull was born in 1340, in Devon, England, his father, Robert Stighull, was 21 and his mother, Muriel Thorber, was 18. He married Elizabeth de Malston in 1365. They were the parents of at least 1 son and 1 daughter. He died in 1397, in England, United Kingdom, at the age of 57."},"et":{"1340–1397":"1340–1397","1344–1394":"1344–1394","1370–Male":"1370–Surnud","1374–Female":"1374–Surnud","1320–1372":"1320–1372","1322–1375":"1322–1375","1374":"1374","1340":"1340","1394":"1394","1372":"1372","1382":"1382","1370":"1370","Abt 1372":"umbes 1372","1322":"1322","1344":"1344","1365":"1365","1397":"1397","1375":"1375","1320":"1320","about 1375":"umbes 1375",", Devon, , England":"Devon, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Devonshire, England":"Devon, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","England":"Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Devon, England":"Devon, England"},"fi":{"1340–1397":"1340–1397","1344–1394":"1344–1394","1370–Male":"1370–Kuollut","1374–Female":"1374–Kuollut","1320–1372":"1320–1372","1322–1375":"1322–1375","1374":"1374","1340":"1340","1394":"1394","1372":"1372","1382":"1382","1370":"1370","Abt 1372":"noin 1372","1322":"1322","1344":"1344","1365":"1365","1397":"1397","1375":"1375","1320":"1320","about 1375":"noin 1375",", Devon, , England":"Devon, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Devonshire, England":"Devon, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","England":"Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Devon, England":"Devon, England"},"fr":{"1340–1397":"1340–1397","1344–1394":"1344–1394","1370–Male":"1370–Décédé","1374–Female":"1374–Décédée","1320–1372":"1320–1372","1322–1375":"1322–1375","1374